title: June Debuts: Attend, for thou shalt cease Not Reading, sayeth me
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.

The month being June 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, obviously.

This instalment contains:


   COWL                    #1 - Image Comics - Historical / Noir / Superhero

   Eye of Newt             #1 - Dark Horse   - Adventure / Fantasy / Traditional

   Henchmen Inc            #1 - Monkeybrain  - Crime / Drama / Superhero

   Princess Ugg            #1 - Oni Press    - Adventure / Fantasy / Humour

   Red City                #1 - Image Comics - Mystery / Neo-Noir / Sci-Fi

   The Wicked + The Divine #1 - Image Comics - Mystery / Pop Culture / Supernatural

   Trees                   #1 - Image Comics - Dystopian / Mystery / Sci-Fi


As a bonus, I re-included one of last month's offerings, because the extent to which it parallels one of this month's in terms of not merely title and basic premise, but a whole slew of conceptual and structural details, seems truly uncanny. Or maybe this is simply the most obvious approach to the subject matter at hand? (Or maybe they're not quite as genuinely unconnected as would appear to be the case at first glance??)
